# Codev
.agent-farm/
.consult/
codev/.update-hashes.json
# porch per-project consult artifacts (rebuttals, context, revision briefs) — intermediate
# process output, not deliverables (the review distills them; specs/plans/reviews + codev/state/
# threads are the durable record). status.yaml is porch's own committed state — keep it tracked.
codev/projects/*/*
!codev/projects/*/status.yaml
.builders/
.architect-role.md

